						<div class="postbody">I've heard lots of great things about using breakpoints, and I really want to learn how to use them. But every time I try set one up, for some reason I can't ever get it to work. I'm just not sure how to go about doing it. For example, how would I go about setting it up to stop when it encounters "STX $102" or something like that?</div>

